            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EHow%20easily%20the%20flesh%20can%20concoct%20a%20religious%20scheme%20that%20appears%20to%20please%20God%20but%20in%20reality%20is%20a%20foolish%20spectacle!%20The%20Levite%20left%20the%20proper%20place%20of%20worship%20at%20the%20tabernacle%20and%20went%20out%20as%20a%20hired%20%22priest%22%20for%20an%20idol%20worshiper.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EReligion%20drifts%20away%20from%20God%20and%20toward%20idolatry%20because%20of%20the%20love%20of%20power%20and%20money.%20The%20further%20religion%20deviates%20from%20God's%20Word%2C%20the%20more%20accepted%20it%20is%20by%20society.%20Flesh%20gives%20birth%20to%20flesh%2C%20and%20soon%20a%20system%20of%20religion%20is%20developed%20that%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Word%20of%20God.%20%22That%20which%20is%20born%20of%20the%20flesh%20is%20flesh%3B%20and%20that%20which%20is%20born%20of%20the%20Spirit%20is%20spirit%22%20(John%203%3A6%20KJV).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJesus%20taught%20Nicodemus%20that%20knowing%20God%20was%20as%20simple%20as%20the%20Holy%20Spirit's%20giving%20him%20a%20new%20birth%20(v.%208).%20Yet%20Nicodemus%2C%20in%20his%20human%20mind%2C%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20more%20complicated.%20Our%20minds%20long%20to%20do%20something%20religious%20to%20earn%20salvation.%20If%20earning%20salvation%20is%20hard%2C%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20it's%20the%20plan%20of%20man.%20If%20it%20is%20simple%2C%20it's%20the%20truth%20of%20God.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEveryone%20can%20easily%20receive%20God's%20salvation%2C%20for%20it%20is%20available%20to%20all.%20Don't%20try%20to%20find%20God%20with%20your%20natural%20mind.%20Instead%2C%20follow%20the%20way%20of%20the%20Spirit!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
